@base=http://localhost:5000

### Genre route teste
### Fetch all genres
GET {{base}}/api/genres

### Fetch specific genre using ID
GET {{base}}/api/genres/65a69236c71e1fcc91c11b0e

### Create new genre
POST {{base}}/api/genres/
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "romance",
  "tags": [
    "tearjerker"
  ]
}

### Update genre using ID
PUT {{base}}/api/genres/65a6936eb0375327db8ab889
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "rom-com"
}

### Self explanatory
DELETE {{base}}/api/genres/65a6936eb0375327db8ab889


### Customers route tests
### Fetch all customers
GET {{base}}/api/customers

### Fetch specific customer using ID
GET {{base}}/api/customers/65a81f7d7057d93b37e5cd58

### Create new customer
POST {{base}}/api/customers
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "isGold": true,
  "name": "Taylor Swift",
  "phone": "+5559876"
}

### Update existing customer based on ID. It is possible to update a single field, or multiple at once.
PUT {{base}}/api/customers/65a821b9efc40a7ef4db9665
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "isGold": false
}

### Delete customer from DB
DELETE {{base}}/api/customers/65a821b9efc40a7ef4db9665